Ever wonder why some lipsticks just don’t work on you? I finally cracked the code at a K-beauty event with @foy_foryou, where a colour analysis revealed my perfect makeup and wardrobe shades- turns out I’m a Warm Spring, like most Indian skin tones. Bright corals, deep yellows, and white tones work best for this palette.

If you’ve ever felt stuck with makeup that doesn’t flatter, this might be exactly what you need. Watch the full reel to see how it works.

Discovering and trying new homegrown brands is one of my biggest joys, but let’s be honest, there are still moments I wonder, “Is it really worth the buy?”
That’s exactly why I started this: to share what I’ve learned and help you shop smarter.
Because let’s face it, homegrown labels often bring something truly special to the table, something fast fashion just can’t replicate.
Think of these homegrown brand reviews as your personal guide to navigating the world of Indian fashion, one thoughtful purchase at a time!
